*Larson, Richard. and Yamakido, Hiroko. (2006) ''"Zazaki as Double Case-Marking"'' [[石溪大学|石溪大学]] and [[亚利桑那大学|亚利桑那大学]],[https://web.archive.org/web/20060903194234/http://semlab5.sbs.sunysb.edu/~rlarson/lsa06ly.pdf].
*Iremet, Faruk. (1996)  "The difference between Zaza, Kurdish and Turkish"  [[斯德哥尔摩|斯德哥尔摩]], [[瑞典|瑞典]],[http://zazapress.tripod.com/english/English.html#farukiremet] {{Wayback|url=http://zazapress.tripod.com/english/English.html#farukiremet |date=20100219213259 }}.
